channel.title: Rate music videos
channel.description:
i got bored and decided to do something odd. I don't consider this advertising at all since the links i will post are all youtube and the youtube videos do not advertise anything other than youtube :p.
Rate the music videos of the songs i listen to and in the end the highest rated will be used in my music video for this year :p i know this is really random GET USED TO IT THIS IS THE GENERAL SECTION, flaming is pointless.
Somewhere i belong - linkin park - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-f__KyX6RiA I hate everything about you - three days grace - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1t9K9rM1SVE Enter in the sandman - metallica - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1QP-SIW6iKY Basket case - greenday - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hitMpM-P-Bs never take us alive - madina lake - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TmxFG5xcxL4
if you think i need to add more send me a YOUTUBE link of any music you think i should add
